title: GraphicConverter v7.6.1 MacOSX Incl Keymaker-CORE
description:
GraphicConverter v7.6.1 MacOSX Incl Keymaker-CORE

Version 7.6.1 (Build 403) released January 20, 2012

New features
added option to display browser preview without alpha channel
Updated features
dcraw updated
Spanish translation enhanced
improved highlights and shadows
reduced memory usage during display of thumbnails and previews in the browser
Bug fixes



Compatibility to Mac OS X 10.7 (Lion):
GraphicConverter 7.3 or later does support the new Lion features
all other products are compatible with Lion

Compatibility to Mac OS X 10.6 (Snow Leopard):
GraphicConverter 6.4 or later is compatible
CADintosh 6.1.1 or later is compatible
FontBook 4.5 or later is compatible
SnapsCleaner 1.3 or later is compatible

Program languages: German, English, French, Danish, Sweden, Italian, Spanish, Japanese, Chinese (simplified), Chinese (traditional), Czech, Dutch, Catalan and Russian.
